Invocation Name: time stream
des:
Test your knowledge of different events across history.

Time Stream provides a fun way to keep your historic event skills sharp.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Time Stream" or "Alexa, open Time Stream" to start the game.

At any time, you can stop the game by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
